---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import StatusLight from "../components/StatusLight.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="About Me">
  <section class="about">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Infrastructure Engineer · Security Architect · Agentic Engineer</p>
    </header>

    <div class="profile">

      <div class="profile-details">
        <div class="detail">
          <span class="detail-label">Location</span>
          <span class="detail-value">New Port Richey, FL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail">
          <span class="detail-label">Status</span>
          <span class="detail-value green"><StatusLight status="ongoing" /> Building secure systems</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail">
          <span class="detail-label">Education</span>
          <span class="detail-value">M.S. Cybersecurity Intelligence @ USF (in progress)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <p class="summary">
        From DOS commands in elementary school to designing enterprise SOC architectures. My path to
        technology wasn't a straight line, but every detour added depth to how I approach problems today.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-header">History</h2>
      <p class="section-comment">A non-linear path to infrastructure and security</p>

      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-entry">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="entry-header">
              <span class="entry-date">~1995-2005</span>
              <span class="entry-title">Early Tech</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Grew up one of ten kids in a household where technology was second nature. My father, a chemical
              engineer and software developer, had me understanding the significance of C and C++ before middle school.
              I became the family's de facto IT department, troubleshooting DOS while other kids were still
              figuring out Windows 95.
            </p>
            <p>
              That foundation led to my first ventures: a web design business during the GeoCities and Angelfire era,
              building custom sites, migrating layouts to PHP, and helping clients claim their corner of the early web.
              I also ran a side operation building and repairing PCs, learning hardware from the ground up.
            </p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">DOS</span>
              <span class="tag">HTML</span>
              <span class="tag">PHP</span>
              <span class="tag">Hardware</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="entry-header">
              <span class="entry-date">2005-2021</span>
              <span class="entry-title">Culinary Detour</span>
            </div>
            <p>
              Life took an unexpected fork. For 17 years, I worked as a cook and chef. A career that seems worlds
              apart from network engineering. But kitchens and server rooms share more than you'd think: both
              demand precision under pressure, systematic thinking, and the ability to troubleshoot on the fly
              when everything's on fire (sometimes literally).
            </p>
            <p>
              Managing kitchen operations taught me workflow optimization, resource allocation, and leading
              teams through high-stakes situations. Skills that translate directly to incident response and
              infrastructure management.
            </p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Leadership</span>
              <span class="tag">Operations</span>
              <span class="tag">Crisis Management</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry current">
          <div class="timeline-marker active"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <div class="entry-header">
              <span class="entry-date">2021-Present</span>
              <span class="entry-title">Return to Root</span>
              <StatusLight status="ongoing" />
            </div>
            <p>
              In 2021, I made the decision to return to my original calling. Enrolled at Polk State College
              for Network Systems Engineering, then continued to a B.A.S. in Business Information Technology.
              Now pursuing an M.S. in Cybersecurity Intelligence at the University of South Florida.
            </p>
            <p>
              Currently working as a Network and Systems Engineer at Polk State, where I design lab environments,
              manage virtualization infrastructure, and build the tools my team needs to operate. The goal:
              bridge the gap between hands-on engineering and strategic security.
            </p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Proxmox</span>
              <span class="tag">Linux</span>
              <span class="tag">Windows Server</span>
              <span class="tag">Security</span>
              <span class="tag">Networking</span>
              <span class="tag">AI Pipelines</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="section-header">Skills</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3 class="skill-label">Infrastructure</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Proxmox VE</span>
            <span class="tag">ESXi</span>
            <span class="tag">Hyper-V</span>
            <span class="tag">Active Directory</span>
            <span class="tag">Samba</span>
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tag">10G Networking</span>
            <span class="tag">LACP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3 class="skill-label">Security</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Wazuh</span>
            <span class="tag">TheHive</span>
            <span class="tag">Cortex</span>
            <span class="tag">MISP</span>
            <span class="tag">Zeek</span>
            <span class="tag">Suricata</span>
            <span class="tag">MITRE ATT&CK</span>
            <span class="tag">Threat Hunting</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3 class="skill-label">Development</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">React</span>
            <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="tag">Python</span>
            <span class="tag">FastAPI</span>
            <span class="tag">Astro</span>
            <span class="tag">Vite</span>
            <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
            <span class="tag">MCP Servers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-group">
          <h3 class="skill-label">AI & Automation</h3>
          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag">Claude Opus</span>
            <span class="tag">GPT</span>
            <span class="tag">Gemini</span>
            <span class="tag">Multi-Model Pipelines</span>
            <span class="tag">Prompt Engineering</span>
            <span class="tag">CI/CD</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section nav-section">
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/experience" class="nav-link">Experience</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="nav-link">Projects</a>
        <a href="/hire" class="nav-link">Hire Me</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
    max-width: 56rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .profile {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border);
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", monospace;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .profile-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .detail {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .detail-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    min-width: 100px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .detail-value.green {
    color: var(--primary);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .summary {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 58ch;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
  }

  .section-comment {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 6px;
    top: 8px;
    bottom: 8px;
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .timeline-entry {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-entry:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 6px;
    width: 13px;
    height: 13px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-marker.active {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 20%, transparent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .timeline-content {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .timeline-content:hover {
    border-color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .timeline-entry.current .timeline-content {
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 25%, transparent);
  }

  .entry-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .entry-date {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .entry-title {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    max-width: 58ch;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .timeline-content p:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .skill-group {
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .skill-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    color: var(--primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .nav-section {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--border);
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .nav-link {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--card-bg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {


    .detail {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.15rem;
    }

    .detail-label {
      min-width: auto;
    }

    .timeline {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      left: -1.5rem;
    }

    .skills-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .nav-links {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
